<div class="card">
  <div class="card-title">Criar lead (demos)</div>
  <p class="muted mt-8">Crie um lead de demonstracao e simule acoes do funil para calcular score automaticamente.</p>
  <div class="card-sub mt-12">Atalhos inteligentes por status (ML)</div>
  <p class="muted mt-8">
    Clique em um dos atalhos para preencher automaticamente o perfil, criar o lead e calcular o score com o modelo de ML em producao.
  </p>
  <div class="quick-preset-grid mt-12">
    <button id="clQuickCurioso" class="btn btn-ghost" type="button">Gerar CURIOSO</button>
    <button id="clQuickAquecendo" class="btn btn-ghost" type="button">Gerar AQUECENDO</button>
    <button id="clQuickQualificado" class="btn btn-ghost" type="button">Gerar QUALIFICADO</button>
  </div>
  <p class="muted mt-8">
    Cada atalho tenta ate 3 perfis automaticamente para aumentar a chance de atingir o status alvo sem perder a consistencia do ML.
  </p>

  <form id="createLeadDemoForm" class="mt-12">
    <div class="lead-demo-form-grid">
      <label class="field">
        <span>Nome</span>
        <input id="clNome" class="input" type="text" value="Visitante Demo" maxlength="120" />
      </label>

      <label class="field">
        <span>UF</span>
        <select id="clUf" class="input">
          <option value="MG">MG</option>
          <option value="SP">SP</option>
          <option value="GO">GO</option>
        </select>
      </label>

      <label class="field">
        <span>WhatsApp (opcional)</span>
        <input
          id="clWhatsapp"
          class="input"
          type="tel"
          inputmode="numeric"
          maxlength="10"
          placeholder="91234-5678"
        />
        <small class="muted">Digite apenas o numero de contato (sem 55 e sem DDD). Ex.: 91234-5678.</small>
      </label>

      <label class="field">
        <span>Cidade (opcional)</span>
        <input id="clCidade" class="input" type="text" maxlength="120" />
      </label>

      <label class="field">
        <span>E-mail (opcional)</span>
        <input id="clEmail" class="input" type="email" maxlength="160" />
      </label>

      <label class="field">
        <span>Segmento de interesse</span>
        <select id="clSegmento" class="input">
          <option value="CAVALOS">CAVALOS</option>
          <option value="SERVICOS">SERVICOS</option>
          <option value="EVENTOS">EVENTOS</option>
          <option value="EQUIPAMENTOS">EQUIPAMENTOS</option>
        </select>
      </label>

      <label class="field">
        <span>Faixa de orcamento</span>
        <select id="clOrcamento" class="input">
          <option value="">-</option>
          <option value="0-5k">0-5k</option>
          <option value="5k-20k">5k-20k</option>
          <option value="20k-60k">20k-60k</option>
          <option value="60k+">60k+</option>
        </select>
      </label>

      <label class="field">
        <span>Prazo</span>
        <select id="clPrazo" class="input">
          <option value="">-</option>
          <option value="7d">7d</option>
          <option value="30d">30d</option>
          <option value="90d">90d</option>
        </select>
      </label>
    </div>

    <h3 class="h3 mt-16">Simular acoes do funil (para o score fazer sentido)</h3>
    <div class="grid grid-3 mt-12">
      <label class="field">
        <span><input id="clEvPageView" type="checkbox" checked /> Visita (page view)</span>
      </label>
      <label class="field">
        <span><input id="clEvHook" type="checkbox" checked /> Completou o quiz/calculadora (hook)</span>
      </label>
      <label class="field">
        <span><input id="clEvCta" type="checkbox" checked /> Clique no CTA/WhatsApp</span>
      </label>
    </div>

    <div class="btn-row mt-16">
      <button id="clSubmitBtn" class="btn" type="submit">Criar lead e simular funil</button>
      <button id="clResetBtn" class="btn btn-ghost" type="button">Limpar</button>
    </div>
  </form>

  <div id="clNotice" class="k-message mt-12" style="display:none;"></div>
</div>

<div id="clResultCard" class="card mt-16" style="display:none;">
  <div class="card-title">Resultado</div>
  <p id="clLeadSummary" class="muted mt-8"></p>

  <div id="clScoreNotice" class="k-message mt-12" style="display:none;"></div>
  <div id="clMlDiag" class="k-message mt-12" style="display:none;"></div>

  <div id="clScoreKpis" class="kpi-row mt-12"></div>

  <h3 class="h3 mt-16">Motivos principais</h3>
  <ul id="clReasonsList" class="list mt-12"></ul>
</div>

<div class="card mt-16">
  <div class="card-title">Roteiro de demo (pitch)</div>
  <p class="muted mt-8">
    Cria automaticamente 3 leads (QUALIFICADO, AQUECENDO e CURIOSO) com tentativa inteligente por status e diagnóstico do modelo de ML.
  </p>

  <div class="btn-row mt-16">
    <button id="clPitchScenarioBtn" class="btn" type="button">Criar cenario de demo (3 leads)</button>
    <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/leads">Ir para Leads</a>
  </div>

  <div id="clPitchNotice" class="k-message mt-12" style="display:none;"></div>
  <div id="clPitchSummary" class="k-matches mt-12" style="display:none;"></div>
</div>

<div class="card mt-16">
  <div class="card-title">Gerar massa de leads (treino ML)</div>
  <p class="muted mt-8">
    Cria uma base sintetica com distribuicao realista de status (CURIOSO, AQUECENDO, QUALIFICADO, ENVIADO).
  </p>

  <div class="grid grid-2 mt-12">
    <label class="field">
      <span>Quantidade de leads</span>
      <input id="clBulkN" class="input" type="number" min="1" max="3000" value="450" />
    </label>

    <label class="field">
      <span>&nbsp;</span>
      <span><input id="clBulkReplace" type="checkbox" /> Limpar leads atuais antes de gerar</span>
    </label>
  </div>

  <div class="btn-row mt-16">
    <button id="clBulkSeedBtn" class="btn btn-ghost" type="button">Gerar massa de leads</button>
    <button id="clBulkResetBtn" class="btn btn-ghost" type="button">Resetar apenas leads sinteticos</button>
    <a class="btn" href="/leads">Ir para Leads</a>
  </div>

  <div id="clBulkNotice" class="k-message mt-12" style="display:none;"></div>
  <p id="clBulkSummary" class="muted mt-8"></p>
</div>

